4ca1468e78e","tid":2260434,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"好心民煮黨咪咁撚無聊"},{"pid":"7c18064088639831775856068d764cddb9869f9d","tid":2260434,"uid":88133,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1159e07853016c9b7ca96b6b672692851ea16f8c","tid":2260434,"uid":165028,"like":24,"dislike":275,"score":-251,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧不嬲都賤格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"都唔夠你個名賤格"},{"pid":"243cf7d8ebbc6b69455b902cb3eaac3862e3b26d","tid":2260434,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"會員 #165028 - 何東精神（團結）<br />\n，前稱純正港人(港豬)，離地中產，天安門旅遊，Frizzle(港豬)，Alexander(離地)極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 好怕d勇武派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車<br />\n<br />\n#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想報仇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767121</a><br />\n<br />\n發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰"},{"pid":"d0aae166a33efd638395088db1d656ce6155e3c4","tid":2260434,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n咁不如話現總統唔撚比選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a81fb2b684f92f451c0963e9bd9ca029a8f74da","tid":2260434,"uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1159e07853016c9b7ca96b6b672692851ea16f8c","tid":2260434,"uid":165028,"like":24,"dislike":275,"score":-251,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧不嬲都賤格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問英德納雄耐爾(狗隻#165028)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767140\" data-auto-link target